Thank you for downloading Manqueef's Queefin' Map Pack #1!

This pack is full of only best and juiciest maps made by Manqueef/Emeriastone to fully satisfy your fetish for red and blue themed maps! Forget those other maps I've made, these are the cream of the crop! 8 of the finest maps ever developed on my dinky PC! 

Like custom textures? Like strange, new, and exciting environments? Like red? Like blue? Like shiny things? Lolcats? This map pack is for you! 

You won't be dissapointed! These maps are sure to please any gun game enthusiast! 

------------
FEATURING: 

gg_annular
gg_circuit
gg_ducksoup
gg_lolcats
gg_metal
gg_orrery
gg_vast
gg_vertex
------------

These maps also have buy-zones for anyone who wishes to have them on any non-gungame server.

gg_orrery and gg_annular developed by RadLionheart and Manqueef/Emeriastone
All textures created/shopped by myself, excluding those skybox textures created by Karatekaefer *sehr Spitze!*

208.146.44.32:27015

Thank you!
